com.djrapitops.plugin.config

Class ConfigNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.djrapitops.plugin.config.ConfigNode
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Config, ConfigNode

    public class ConfigNode
extends Object
    Represents a single node in a Config.

    Can be used to copy default values to other config nodes with copyDefaults(ConfigNode).

    Author:
    Rsl1122

      • copyDefaults

        public void copyDefaults(ConfigNode node)
        Copy default values from a node if no values exist for this node.

        Non-existing nodes will be added from the given node. Depth-first.

        Values are only held in memory unless save() is called.

        Parameters:
        node - Node to copy things from.
